node.text:
[#TheHedgehogAtHome] Oops. Caught trying to pinch that slice of Margherita Pizza. 😅
.
This classic pizza (S$26.17), from @RegentSingapore, was topped generous with lots of mozzarella cheese and fresh basil leaves. Yums! Available for takeaway and delivery.
